    (12980, 'brittle', 'TOEFL_2', '易碎的, 脆弱的', 'adj', '''brɪtl', '''brɪt(ə)l', 'In systems such as this we also often find that there are either no tests around this configuration code, or the tests that do exist are brittle and/or not realistic.', '在这样的系统中，我们经常会发现对于这些配置代码没有进行测试，或者尽管存在测试，但它很脆弱且/或不切实际。'),
