    (12992, 'ibex', 'TOEFL_2', '野生山羊', 'n', '''aɪbɛks', '''aɪbeks', 'Other common forms of synecdoche include two concentric circles or triangles (used as eyes in horse and bison paintings), ibex horns and the hump of a mammoth.', '其他普通的提喻形式包括两个同心圆或者三角形（在壁画上马和犀牛的眼睛里也有使用），野生山羊的羊角和长毛象弓起的背部。'),
