    (13003, 'snowdrift', 'TOEFL_2', '雪堆', 'n', '''snodrɪft', '''snəʊdrɪft', 'Weller was once a stranded motorist himself. Driving in an Illinois blizzard when he was 16, he got stuck in a snowdrift.', '韦勒自己曾经也是一个无助驾驶员，在他16岁的时候驾驶在伊利诺斯州的暴风雪中，陷入了雪堆。'),
