    (13037, 'watercourses', 'TOEFL_2', '水流, 河道', 'n', '''wɔtɚkɔrs', '''wɔːtəkɔːs', 'This often results in huge holes in the ground, noxious spoil-heaps and polluted watercourses.', '这常常会在地面上留下一个个巨大的坑，有毒的矸子山和污染的河道.'),
