    (13252, 'eject', 'TOEFL_2', '逐出,喷射', 'v', 'ɪ''dʒɛkt', 'ɪ''dʒekt', 'Two engines cut out and the plane started to eject fuel as it lost height.', '两个发动机突然熄火，飞机在下降的同时开始喷出燃料。'),
