    (13259, 'ptarmigan', 'TOEFL_2', '松鸡类', 'n', '''tɑrmɪɡən', '''tɑːmɪg(ə)n', 'It was a fearful cry, but the fox, leaping away in fright, did not drop the ptarmigan.', '这是一种可怕的喊声，那只狐狸吓跑了，可是没有丢下松鸡。'),
