    (13261, 'rapidity', 'TOEFL_2', '速度,迅速,急速', 'n', 'rə''pɪdəti', 'rə''pɪdɪtɪ', 'And it is from this extended sense of connection that the magnitude of changes, the rapidity of changes, can truly begin to take place.', '并且在这扩展延伸的连接感觉当中强度会发生改变，而且是迅速的改变，这会真实的开始并且发生。'),
