    (13301, 'recommendation', 'TOEFL_2', '推荐, 介绍(信)', 'n', ',rɛkəmɛn''deʃən', ',rekəmen''deɪʃ(ə)n', 'Try to get letters of recommendation from bosses and colleagues.', '设法得到老板和同事的推荐信。'),
