    (13660, 'correlate', 'TOEFL_2', '相互关联', 'v', '''kɔrəlet', '''kɒrəleɪt; -rɪ-', 'Attempts to correlate specific language functions with particular parts of the brain have not advanced very far.', '试图把特定的语言功能和大脑特定区域相联系的努力还没有取得很大进展。'),
