    (13662, 'glial', 'TOEFL_2', '神经胶质的', 'adj', '''ɡlaɪə', '''ɡlaɪəl', 'The glial tissue is where the largest percentage of brain tumors begin.', '胶质组织是绝大多数脑部肿瘤的起源。'),
    (13663, 'autonomic', 'TOEFL_2', '自治的, 自律的', 'adj', ',ɔtə''nɑmɪk', ',ɔːtə''nɒmɪk', 'Concepts such as autonomic computing will have a key role in cloud storage architectures in the future.', '在未来，诸如自主计算这样的概念将在云存储架构中起到关键的作用。'),
