    (13669, 'proboscis', 'TOEFL_2', '鼻子,[昆] 喙', 'n', 'pro''bɑsɪs', 'prə''bɒsɪs', 'At least they didn''t give me a butterfly''s proboscis, or crab mandibles.', '至少他们没有给我一只蝴蝶的鼻子，或者一只螃蟹的下颌。'),
