    (15845, 'overheat', 'TOEFL_2', '使过热， 变得过热', 'v', ',ovɚ''hit', 'əʊvə''hiːt', 'I think the engine’s overheating again.', '我想引擎又过热了。'),
    (15846, 'efficacy', 'TOEFL_2', '功效, 效验', 'n', '''ɛfɪkəsi', '''efɪkəsɪ', 'Recent medical studies confirm the efficacy of a healthier lifestyle.', '近来的医学研究证实了更健康的生活方式的功效。'),
    (15847, 'dilution', 'TOEFL_2', '稀释', 'n', 'dɪ''ljʊʃən', 'daɪ''luːʃn', '"Aromatherapy oils" are not pure essential oils but dilutions.', '“香薰精油”不是纯精油，而是稀释油。'),
    (15848, 'festive', 'TOEFL_2', '庆祝的, 喜庆的', 'adj', '''fɛstɪv', '''festɪv', 'The atmosphere was festive and jolly.', '气氛喜庆欢乐。'),
    (15849, 'zealous', 'TOEFL_2', '热心的', 'adj', '''zɛləs', '''zeləs', 'a zealous preacher', '热心的讲道者'),
    (15850, 'bust', 'TOEFL_2', '半身像, 胸像', 'n', 'bʌst', 'bʌst', 'a 36-inch bust', '36英寸的胸围'),
    (15851, 'equestrian', 'TOEFL_2', '骑马的 n骑手', 'adj', 'ɪ''kwɛstrɪən', 'ɪ''kwestrɪən; e-', 'equestrian sports', '马术运动'),
    (15852, 'urn', 'TOEFL_2', '瓮, 缸', 'n', 'ɝn', 'ɜːn', '...a funeral urn.', '…一个骨灰瓮。'),
    (15853, 'timidity', 'TOEFL_2', '胆怯', 'n', 'tɪ''mɪdəti', 'tɪ''mɪdətɪ', 'They mocked at my timidity.', '他们耻笑我胆小。'),
    (15854, 'stonemason', 'TOEFL_2', '石匠', 'n', '''stonmesn', '''stəʊnmeɪs(ə)n', 'One thinks of Amos the sheepherder, Socrates the stonemason, Omar the tentmaker .', '想想牧羊人阿摩司，石匠苏格拉底，帐蓬制造人奥马尔。'),
    (15855, 'biter', 'TOEFL_2', '咬人的动物, 骗子', 'n', '''baɪtɚ', '''baɪtə', 'The kids already know that biting hurts, so after removing the biter from the situation, focus all your concern on the victim.', '孩子是知道咬会伤人的，因此把咬人的孩子抱离后，集中关心一下被咬的孩子。'),
    (15856, 'bitterness', 'TOEFL_2', '苦味, 辛酸', 'n', '''bɪtɚnɪs', 'bɪtənəs', 'ON WHY THE POOR SHOULD BE HAPPY: “Nobody has the excuse of ‘lack of money’ for not being at peace and living in integrity,” writes one survey respondent of his family, with a touch of bitterness.', '关于为什么穷人应该是快乐的：“没有人会因为没有钱这个借口而过的不平和和不完整，”某个调查对象在说到关于他的家庭的时候，带着一点痛苦的意味。'),
    (15857, 'aero', 'TOEFL_2', '航空的,  飞行的', 'adj', '''ɛro', '''eərəʊ', 'Boeing''s research in India will break new ground in aero structures, aerodynamics and electronic networks with a team of senior researchers, scientists and engineers.', '在印度，波音公司将与资深研究人员、科学家和工程师一起开创印度航空构造学、空气动力学以及电子网络的新天地。'),
    (15858, 'thorny', 'TOEFL_2', '多刺的, 痛苦的', 'adj', '''θɔrni', '''θɔːnɪ', '...thorny hawthorn trees.', '…带刺的山楂树。'),
    (15859, 'inchworm', 'TOEFL_2', '[昆] 尺蠖', 'n', '''ɪntʃwɝm', '''ɪn(t)ʃwɜːm', 'The adorable inchworm is really the caterpillar of the geometer moth.', '可爱的尺蠖就是尺蠖毛虫。'),
    (15860, 'escalator', 'TOEFL_2', '电动扶梯', 'n', '''ɛskə''letɚ', '''eskəleɪtə', 'Take the escalator to the third floor and it''s the last office on the left.', '乘电梯到4楼，左边最后的那个办公室就是。'),
    (15861, 'voltage', 'TOEFL_2', '[电工]电压, 伏特数', 'n', '''voltɪdʒ', '''vəʊltɪdʒ; ''vɒltɪdʒ', 'The systems are getting smaller and using lower voltages.', '这些系统正变得更小而且使用更低的电压。'),
    (15862, 'smite', 'TOEFL_2', '重击', 'v', 'smaɪt', 'smaɪt', 'The heroic leader charged into battle, ready to smite the enemy.', '英勇的军官冲上战场，准备重击敌人。'),
    (15863, 'follower', 'TOEFL_2', '追随者, 信徒', 'n', '''fɑloɚ', '''fɒləʊə', 'Marx and his followers were convinced that capitalism would destroy itself.', '马克思及其支持者确信资本主义将自我毁灭。'),
    (15864, 'indifference', 'TOEFL_2', '不关心', 'n', 'ɪn''dɪfrəns', 'ɪn''dɪf(ə)r(ə)ns', 'Whether you stay or leave is a matter of total indifference to me (= I do not care ).', '你是留是走我根本无所谓。'),
    (15865, 'eyelid', 'TOEFL_2', '眼皮, 眼睑', 'n', '''aɪ,lɪd', '''aɪlɪd', 'His eyelids began to droop (= close, because he was sleepy ).', '他的眼皮开始往下垂。'),
    (15866, 'comfortably', 'TOEFL_2', '舒适地', 'adv', '''kʌmftəbli', '''kʌmfətəbli', 'The hotel is modern and comfortably furnished .', '这家宾馆很现代化，家具很舒适。'),
    (15867, 'hatchet', 'TOEFL_2', '短柄斧', 'n', '''hætʃɪt', '''hætʃɪt', 'Would I feel better if I took a hatchet to her, just to end this nightmare?', '如果我向她举起一把短柄斧，结束这场噩梦，我会感觉好一些吗？'),
    (15868, 'attributable', 'TOEFL_2', '可归因于的', 'adj', 'ə''trɪbjətəbl', 'ə''trɪbjʊtəbl', '10,000 deaths a year from chronic lung disease are attributable to smoking.', '每年1万个慢性肺病患者的死亡可能是由于吸烟导致的。'),
